Vietnam like any other nation must have a progressive industrial capability to survive and grow.  They have lost the strength of their communist support block.  They know need the west to survive.<br><br>
Needs modify ideologies.  I believe Vietnam is going down the road of discovery to find how much change is enough to bring the west to their door.<br><br>
They only have to look at the example of North Korea to see what the outcome will be.<br><br>
Money, goods, and material needs of the few will make change for the many.
